Locus:
  Case: 99
Title: The National Teacher Taming and Driving
---
A test is raised for examination/(to) examine it

Emperor Suzong asked National Teacher Zhong, So what is
the The Taming and Driving One of the ten bodies [of
Buddha]?

The National Teacher said, Patron, the supreme practice
of surpassing stepping on Vairocanas crown.

The Emperor said,  solitary person does not
understand.

The National Teacher said,  never recognizes ones
own selfs pure and clear Dharma-body.

Xuedou's ode says
